snippet.textDisplay:
"In ko kho ke um'r bhar na tareste raho - aaj jaanay ki zid na karo"
Agar aunty pehlay bata detein tu kafee tension se farigh rehta. Aunty bhi na... 
Faiz Sb., Sohail uncle, Madam Khanum. This is an example of how a simple melody is turned into a masterpiece by how the lady sings and maneuvers through the tonal structure of the simple composition, making it heart wrenching.
